article_title: Paul Wilson: 2015 was a productive year for Olmsted County
article_text:
Rochester, MN (55903)

Today

Cloudy early, then thunderstorms developing this afternoon. High near 75F. Winds SSE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 100%..

Tonight

Cloudy skies this evening followed by thunderstorms late. A few storms may be severe. Low 62F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: Paul Wilson

og.description: With all of the growth and changes coming, I have referred to 2015 as "the year of opportunities." As a new year begins, I would like to offer a recap
